<h2>Someone is interested in your found item!</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @found_item.contact_name %>,</p>

<p>Someone has reached out regarding your found item post.</p>

<h3><strong><%= @found_item.title %></strong></h3>

<p><strong>Sender's Name:</strong> <%= @sender_name %></p>
<p><strong>Sender's Email:</strong> <%= @sender_email %></p>

<h3>Message:</h3>
<p><%= simple_format(@message) %></p>

<hr>

<p>You can reply directly to <strong><%= @sender_email %></strong> to continue the conversation.</p>

<p>---<br>
Northwestern Lost and Found Board<br>
<%= link_to "View this item", found_item_url(@found_item) %>
</p>
